<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #3b82f6;">Agreement Ready for Your Signature</h2>

    <p>Hi <%= @recipient.name %>,</p>

    <p>The seller has signed the trade agreement for Trade #<%= @trade.id %>. Your signature is now required to proceed.</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Trade Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Item:</strong> <%= @trade.item&.name %></p>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@trade.price / 100.0) %></p>
      <p><strong>Seller:</strong> <%= @trade.seller.name %></p>
    </div>

    <% if @trade_document&.expires_at.present? %>
      <div style="background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>‚è∞ Signature Deadline:</strong> <%= l(@trade_document.expires_at, format: :long) %></p>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px;">The agreement must be signed before this deadline or the trade will be cancelled.</p>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <p><strong>What You Need to Do:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Review the trade agreement carefully</li>
      <li>Verify all details are correct</li>
      <li>Sign the agreement electronically</li>
      <li>After signing, you'll be able to fund the escrow</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
      <% if @trade_document.present? %>
        <%= link_to "Sign Agreement Now", signing_url_trade_url(@trade), style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "View Trade", trade_url(@trade), style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
      The trade agreement protects both parties and outlines the terms of this transaction. Please review it carefully before signing.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
